trans-unit.source: For the purposes of this calculation, one Test includes any number of Samples that are collected from one Athlete during a single Sample Collection Session. For example, a Sample Collection Session in which one (1) urine Sample and two (2) blood Samples are collected will count as one Test. Blood ABP Tests, conducted in isolation, shall not be included in this calculation.
